item.title: .NET Framework Code Execution Process
item.description: –What is managed and unmanaged code in .NET???? When you write, compile, and run an application, there’s a lot of complex things going on “under the hood” that most developers aren’t able to see or follow. As a developer, I think it’s important to know or atleast have an idea of how your applications are compiled and executed.
